ial. And list any preferred hard and soft skills. Example Auto Mechanic requirements Proven experience working with vehicles Knowledge of machinery, hydraulic, and electrical systems Ability to work on a team High School diploma or GED equivalent Ability to problem solve Good physical strength and stamina Auto Mechanic related job titles: Mechanic Car Mechanic Automotive Technician Car Technician Car Tech Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
